  "description": "{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"96mnm\",\"text\":\"Fixative preparation for Baermann funnel extraction\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{}}",
  "guidelines": "",
